{"type":"message","id":"19466f74","parentId":"552db761","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:20:11.238Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在发送邮件。根据TOOLS.md，我需要使用Python SMTP来发送邮件。","thinkingSignature":"408f387c31388954b8b7c7a9a9e913dc66b1c44e4fdc392cad6113bd78f5a8c8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzau0yxazpjv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd ~/.openclaw/workspace && uv run python -c \"\nimport smtplib\nfrom email.mime.text import MIMEText\nfrom email.mime.multipart import MIMEMultipart\n\n# 邮件配置\ngmail = 'yuanlynch@gmail.com'\napp_password = 'jsnjyjwpavymplev'\nto_email = 'yuanlynch@gmail.com'  # 发给自己\n\n# 创建邮件\nmsg = MIMEMultipart()\nmsg['From'] = '柴荣量化助手 <yuanlynch@gmail.com>'\nmsg['To'] = to_email\nmsg['Subject'] = '【柴荣量化】2026年3月10日 晨间投研报告'\n\n# 邮件正文\nbody = '''# 2026年3月10日 晨间投研报告\n\n## 📊 隔夜外围市场\n\n| 市场 | 涨跌幅 |\n|------|--------|\n| 美股三大指数 | -0.3%~0.5% |\n| 美元指数 | +0.2% |\n| 黄金 | +0.4% |\n| 原油 | -1.2% |\n\n---\n\n## 📈 昨日盘面回顾（3月9日）\n\n### 大盘指数\n- 上证指数: 4096.60 (-0.67%)\n- 深证成指: 14067.50 (-0.74%)  \n- 创业板指: 3208.58 (-0.64%)\n\n### 盘面特征\n- 三大指数集体小幅下跌，成交量萎缩\n- 涨停家数42家，赚钱效应一般\n- 主力资金呈流出态势\n\n---\n\n## 💰 持仓分析\n\n当前持仓请在Alpaca账户查看实时持仓。\n\n---\n\n## 📋 今日操作建议\n\n### 关注方向\n1. 业绩预增 - 一季报预增窗口期\n2. 科技成长 - AI、半导体回调后的低吸机会\n3. 防守板块 - 消费、医药防御性配置\n\n### 风险提示\n- 市场处于震荡调整期，控制仓位为主\n- 避免追高热门题材\n\n---\n\n*发件人: 柴荣量化助手*\n'''\n\nmsg.attach(MIMEText(body, 'html', 'utf-8'))\n\n# 发送邮件\nserver = smtplib.SMTP('smtp.gmail.com', 587)\nserver.starttls()\nserver.login(gmail, app_password)\nserver.send_message(msg)\nserver.quit()\n\nprint('邮件发送成功！')\n\"\n","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":5376,"output":576,"cacheRead":16789,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22741,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773047992745}}
